    <description>Tutanota is the world's most secure email service, easy to use and private by design. Sign up for free encrypted email now.

With end-to-end encryption and 2FA, your emails have never been more secure. The built-in encryption guarantees that your mailbox belongs to you: Nobody can decrypt or read your data.

**Please Note**: This is an automatically updated package. If you find it is out of date by more than a day or two, please contact the maintainer(s) and let them know the package is no longer updating correctly.</description>
    <summary>Tutanota is an email client with a strong focus on security and privacy that lets you encrypt emails on all your devices.</summary>
    <releaseNotes># What's new
 - Always allow creating event repeating on the fourth occurrence of a weekday [#10833](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10833)
 - Handle event and alarm creation as one seamless operation [#10568](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10568)

# Bugfixes
 - Error when duplicating events with alarms [#9887](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/9887)
 - Editing Altered Event choosing this and the future throws an error [#9665](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/9665)

